Matthew J. Shattock



Mr. Matthew J. Shattock is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Beam Suntory, Inc. and President at Jim Beam Brands Co. He is on the Board of Directors at VF Corp. and Suntory Holdings Ltd. Mr. Shattock was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Beam Global Spirits & Wine, Inc., President-Europe Region by Cadbury Plc, Chief Operating Officer-North America Region by Unilever Best Foods, and a Principal by United Kingdom Army. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Durham.



